<div id="comments" class="comment-list hot show">
        <ul>
                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="348880671">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-348880671" class="vote-count">6</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-348880671" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="348880671">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/danyboy/">danyboy</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2011-02-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">典型的现代思想。巴塔耶认为人的禁忌原本为了脱离兽性而创制，但为此才导致色情的产生。所以只有对禁忌进行再否定，解放的将是神性而非兽性。孟子说人之异于禽兽者几希，现代思想连这点“异”都不想要，真是幼稚且危险。所以要感谢孔孟耶稣等圣人立法在前，世人方不至于坠入危险游戏。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="2636757">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-2636757" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-2636757" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="2636757">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chunfeng/">已注销</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
                    <span>2006-04-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
